Description: export PDF pages as image files
 PDF Image Exporter is a graphical GNU/Linux application for converting PDF
 pages to PNG, JPEG or TIFF images using Poppler's pdftocairo tool.
 .
 It supports batch conversion, page ranges, output naming policies, conversion
 profiles, conflict handling and low-resolution previews.
